    &kp Q            &kp W                       &kp E           &kp R               &kp T                   &kp Y                  &kp U               &kp I           &kp O               &kp P
    &hm LSHFT A      &hm LCTRL S                 &hm LALT D      &hm LGUI F          &kp G                   &kp H                  &hm LGUI J          &hm LALT K      &hm LCTRL L         &hm LSHFT SEMI
